1.title: Headliner Special #1 - PSY
1.plot: Mnet America brings you the series premiere of HEADLINER featuring the one and only PSY! You may know K-pop veteran Psy as the global superstar he is now but unlike most success stories, it didn't happen overnight. See how Psy made it to the top!

2.title: Headliner Special #2 - Big Bang
2.plot: Since their debut in 2006, Big Bang have transformed from being just another K-pop group to becoming true global music icons - redefining what it means to be true artists in the K-pop music industry. Mnet America proudly presents Headliner, featuring G-Dragon, Taeyang, T.O.P, Daesung and Seungri. See how they rose to the top to become the trendsetters we know today.

3.title: Headliner Special #3 - Aziatix
3.plot: What happens when three individual superstars join together to form one musically gifted group? Monumental global success. Jay "Flowsik" Pak, Eddie Shin & Nicky Lee better known as the AZIATIX quickly became the first Asian-American hip hop group to be signed to the one and only Cash Money Records.

4.title: U-Kiss Exclusive Interview
4.plot: Hosted by Eli, all 6 members sat down to answer our burning questions and more as they prep for their first U.S. Tour in NY, SF and LA.

5.title: Headliner Special #5 - CNBLUE
5.plot: It's K-pop with a rock-n-roll twist! Mnet America presents another special episode of Headliner with your February stars, CNBLUE. Take a close look into their music career, from no-name street performers to the international super stars as we know them today. Tune in to find out the unique pop-rock band's distinctively music-driven journey to success!

imdb.plot outline: Headliner is a monthly biography series on the most high-profile Kpop stars in the music industry. This is the never-been-told life story of today's hottest artists that gives a behind-the-scenes glance into their trials and tribulations. Follow them on their rolling road to success, fame and ultimate glory.
